summary: WHILE THE VEHICLE WAS PARKED IN A PARKING LOT THE DRIVER SIDE HEAD REST AIRBAG DEPLOYED.  THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO A CHRYSLER DEALERSHIP.  THE DEALERSHIP CONFIRMED NO IMPACT EVENT OCCURRED AND THE BAG JUST DEPLOYED.  DEALER ALSO SAID IT WAS NOT A WARRANTY COVERED ITEM AND WOULD NOT REPLACE/REPAIR AT NOT COST.  ON THE DAY THE BAG DEPLOYED IT WAS A HOT SUNNY DAY.
